## {{ill|Kanshūji Lineage|ja|勧修寺流|12=draft|12=draft}}: From {{ill|Fujiwara no Tamemitsu|ja|藤原為房|12=draft|12=draft}} through {{ill|Fujiwara no Tameyoshi|ja|為隆|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Fujiwara no Mitsumoto|ja|光房|12=draft|12=draft}} (noted as Kadenokōji). Descendant {{ill|Takakiyo Fujiwara|ja|藤原高清|12=draft|12=draft}} is also listed as Kadenokōji in genealogies.
## {{ill|Hino Family|ja|日野家|12=draft|12=draft}} lineage: From {{ill|Hino Sukemasa|ja|日野資長|12=draft|12=draft}} through {{ill|Hino Kanemitsu|ja|藤原兼光|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Hirohashi Yoritsugu|ja|広橋頼資|12=draft|12=draft}} (noted as Kadenokōji). Yoritsugu's descendants, including {{ill|Hirohashi Tsunemitsu|ja|広橋経光|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hirohashi Kanemoto|ja|広橋兼仲|12=draft|12=draft}}, later adopted the name {{ill|Hirohashi|ja|広橋家|12=draft|12=draft}}.
## {{ill|Hino Family|ja|日野家|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Karasumaru Lineage|ja|烏丸流|12=draft|12=draft}}: Refer to {{ill|Kadenokōji Family (Hino lineage)|ja|勘解由小路家 (日野流)|12=draft|12=draft}}.
